Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.80,0:00:50.84,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Slowly, quietly, floating by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:59.53,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}Gently fading into the distant bright sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:08.40,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}More fickle than the wind,\N my goal is beyond it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:11.49,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Let's go together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:17.13,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a breath and skip along,\N the world's spring breath
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.13,0:01:22.68,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun brings all our smiles together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.68,0:01:30.23,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Between "good morning" and "good bye" it's just us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:33.89,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}We can do whatever we want
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.05,0:01:39.99,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}The sunlight shining down,\N a brand new sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:45.73,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The morning arch we promised to meet at
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:53.53,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}Waving your hand at me,\N let me make today a special day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:56.67,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,600)}Let's start by talking
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:30.94,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of scenery do you expect to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:38.86,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there it is, the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:45.28,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,On the burning sand, my heart is dancing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:53.63,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,With every blink, the sun in my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:20:00.09,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like my wanting to play was just hiding away,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:08.31,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,A side of me you've never seen before, running ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:13.56,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue sky in your heart, the waves splashing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:16.15,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,A feeling you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:20.90,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, sisters, the swimsuit tans
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:23.49,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring us together
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:29.41,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,With all the rays we catch,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:34.00,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make a rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.74,0:22:45.91,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Next to me in the sunset, a silhouette tall as me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.91,0:22:54.72,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of another fun day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:23:01.89,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,I've still got so much unending stuff to talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:09.23,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's time for us to go home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.23,0:23:16.40,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, see you tomorrow, I'll text you later
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.40,0:23:23.70,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's page is about all our smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.70,0:23:31.00,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, see you tomorrow, thanks as always
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:39.55,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy we could be together today too
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.55,0:23:46.72,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Humhumhum, the wind and my heart are humming
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.72,0:23:53.98,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}At the next corner, I'll turn around and say "Bye bye"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.42,0:00:07.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.54,0:00:10.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.27,0:00:12.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound so gloomy, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:15.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer! Let's go to the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.86,0:00:21.05,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anyone to see this tiny body.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.05,0:00:23.54,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:28.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has special traits.\N You just need to bring out the best in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:30.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:33.46,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or so a certain kind of people say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:35.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:08.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:11.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you a swimsuit with that in mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:17.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I picked the smallest one they had, so let's go to the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:19.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.15,0:02:25.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it'll look good on you! Try it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:27.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:30.91,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:36.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's kind of loose...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:41.28,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:43.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:46.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:49.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, we have ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't eat anything right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:54.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:56.32,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:59.28,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! This flavor just came out this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:03.20,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too! I thought I might try it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:05.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:07.08,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we split it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.42,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.62,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind! I can eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:19.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:26.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\an5\fs70\fad(400,0)\be4\c&HFADBBC&\pos(640,494)\3c&HCDBBB2&}Beach
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:33.82,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pool time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:35.14,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Changed already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:39.36,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly. You're in high school and you still get excited by the pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:40.90,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be nice to be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:45.07,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? Summer is all about the pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:47.35,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget that we're in class?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:49.21,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pool is the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:55.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Your swimsuit is faded everywhere but here. Is it a hand-me-down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:04:01.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been using this one since elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:11.55,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:14.91,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,This floating feeling is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:17.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your boobs are huge, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:19.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:24.36,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have an easy time swimming with that fat as a flotation device.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:26.50,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounded bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:28.15,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:30.50,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'd never—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:44.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No fat at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.35,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:53.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,P.E. in the summer is just too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:01.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first years have the pool today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:03.00,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.20,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:06.82,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pool looks so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:16.83,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Gather 'round.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:21.59,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:23.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.47,0:05:26.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nagi? Didn't you hate the pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:28.59,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:32.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, I hate wearing swimsuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:33.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:35.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:38.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get water on me! Dump a bucket on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.51,0:05:40.77,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heat's fried Nagi's brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:47.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:49.90,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:54.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Summer vacation starts tomorrow! Let's go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.08,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:01.67,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a swimsuit for the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:04.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to wear a swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:08.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two saying? That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:12.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:17.94,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear that? Just because she has a nice body!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:19.62,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because she has white skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:21.55,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:23.75,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:26.15,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what modesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:28.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:32.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the beach together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:35.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:40.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm hot from walking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:43.00,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to drag you along with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I got myself some stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:47.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about sitting down somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:54.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Do you feel alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:57.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,This wall traps the cool air in this corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:06:59.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sit right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:03.85,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Nagi! Stand up! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:09.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is really big!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:13.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be over 170 centimeters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:16.62,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone must think I'm too big...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:19.18,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:22.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thin, tall, and you've got boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:24.00,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention the boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:27.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty hard living with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:28.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.21,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, these bras are pretty nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:34.25,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're cheap! Maybe I'll get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:37.67,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I want one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:39.93,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.89,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sizes on these are up to D.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:46.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess smaller ones are nice sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:56.62,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't we take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:08:00.42,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Didn't we decide we weren't going to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:02.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, they're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:06.25,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not buying one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:23.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:24.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:25.88,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:29.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'll try it on. Mind seeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:29.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:32.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:33.89,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:36.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:40.91,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:42.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:43.83,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:47.62,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:49.07,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:50.91,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too hard to choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:53.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should check out a few others!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:06.54,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll only be a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.82,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.15,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.34,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, thanks for waiting—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:51.69,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think! I was just looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:57.94,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:01.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I get one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:04.34,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice one, and it looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:05.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:07.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.69,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,A text?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:13.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm inviting Run and Tooru to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:19.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just two kilograms...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.37,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:31.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run says okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:34.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:35.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:37.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan just came by.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:39.62,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she go home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:42.86,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She said she just wanted you to have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:11:00.59,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a swimsuit I used to wear. I think it should fit you perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:22.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's race to that island, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:34.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Play hard and study hard. I look forward to seeing all your bright, shining faces next term.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:49.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:12.24,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beach! Beach! Beach! Beach! Beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:14.88,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.57,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:23.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:27.93,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:38.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's a streetcar, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:42.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:46.57,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty cool. It can run on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:49.07,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did they switch them on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:51.24,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Switch what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:54.09,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the tires.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:56.25,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't use tires.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:10.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:12.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:14.77,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:17.09,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,This beach has me all excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:18.64,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:20.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.32,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for giving me your swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:27.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. I'm glad it fit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:29.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry the design is so kiddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:32.03,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:34.91,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used it in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:38.89,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:40.36,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:41.50,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:47.05,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elementary school...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:57.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:00.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:14.21,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.95,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Have a lift!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:22.57,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:24.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks fun, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:26.83,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:35.87,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru? Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:44.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:46.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:48.03,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seaweed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:52.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good on you, Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:55.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seaweed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:07.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, time-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:09.95,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Nagi? Tired already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:14.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up at five this morning. I'm almost out of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:16.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still going strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:18.10,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, I'm weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.87,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:21.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get some juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:23.94,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me a melon soda?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.32,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:28.85,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sports drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:30.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:37.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:39.62,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:43.00,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have a lot of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:44.62,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:48.38,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:49.84,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:16:00.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I would find that legendary tortoiseshell candy juice here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:03.89,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan, here's your drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:05.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:06.64,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:09.15,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:11.15,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:14.84,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly. She said she was going strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:17.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sit down, and look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:19.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks really relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.66,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:30.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sure feels nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:38.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not many people, and it's so quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:41.37,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,These southern islands are great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.15,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaves?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:57.86,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, Tooru. That tickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:04.95,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:13.11,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:17.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.82,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:31.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,A castle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:34.09,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:35.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:37.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:40.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:42.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:46.29,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:48.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:52.41,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:54.67,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:06.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:09.93,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like you're getting pulled in! It's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:25.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that much fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:29.00,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:40.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:54.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunchtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:57.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach is all about ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:57.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakisoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:19:00.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That southern taste, octopus rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:01.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boxed lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:03.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:04.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:08.10,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:09.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:12.87,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we're at the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:16.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:20.07,hardsub pos,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like people are leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:22.79,hardsub pos,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:25.43,hardsub pos,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like we played all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:27.57,hardsub pos,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we came so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:29.07,hardsub pos,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:31.99,hardsub pos,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach was a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.99,0:20:34.00,hardsub pos,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:37.36,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:39.50,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's come again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.93,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:48.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:50.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.47,0:20:54.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.84,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We get the car to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:04.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan, why don't you sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:06.44,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll stand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:08.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't get back for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:12.20,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I still have a lot of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:20.46,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Yuuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:22.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:24.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cuticle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:27.69,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your cuticle okay, Yuuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:28.95,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:30.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:35.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair is long and pretty, so you have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:36.60,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your skin is white.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:39.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:41.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wonder if I tanned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.68,0:21:43.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:45.88,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We put enough sunscreen on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:47.90,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?\N Run, how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.65,0:21:51.90,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't tanned a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:54.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, what sunscreen do you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:56.91,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't use any.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.37,0:22:00.54,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't use any, and you have this kind of skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:02.75,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:04.54,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.23,0:22:10.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,My skin just doesn't tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.30,0:22:12.03,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:13.55,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an alien or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.55,0:22:16.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:17.59,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan is from Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.59,0:22:18.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.81,0:22:20.37,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:56.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H9E49D6&\3c&HCACFBF&\pos(640,140)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:58.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we get so sleepy after we swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.56,0:24:01.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially those afternoons after swimming in class!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.47,0:24:03.66,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It marks the start of a cycle of terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.66,0:24:04.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.39,0:24:07.25,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you sleep in the afternoon, you can't sleep at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:10.82,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you don't sleep at night, you'll get sleepy in the afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.82,0:24:12.46,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.46,0:24:15.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next A Channel: A Midsummer Night's...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.49,0:24:19.62,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you sleep from afternoon until morning, it all works out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.62,0:24:21.58,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many hours will you sleep?!
